Below is a listing of applications which, subject to the pre-grant notice and petition procedure of Section 309 of the Communications Act of 1934, as amended, were accepted for filing during the week. There may be instances when an application which is listed below has already appeared on an earlier-released Public Notice. In those instances, the Commission will measure time from the date on which the application first appeared on Public Notice. The service designator file number preceding an applicant's name is derived pursuant to Section 1.952 of the Rules. This Public Notice also contains other information concerning items which were filed or acted upon during the period stated.
